nodes.documentation:
@title Handler for transferring plane ownership
 @author Sean Malone, Joseph Nguyen, Nick Vrdoljak
nodes.name: PlaneOwnership

nodes.documentation: emits an event when a transfer occurs
nodes.name: Transfer

nodes.documentation: restricts functions to be called only by the owner of the plane;
nodes.name: onlyOwnerOf

nodes.documentation: returns the number of planes a user owns
nodes.name: balanceOf

nodes.documentation: returns the owner of a particular plane
nodes.name: ownerOf

nodes.documentation: transfers a plan from one address to another - private function to be called only by other functions
nodes.name: _transfer

nodes.documentation: transfers from one address to another, only to be called by the initial owner of the plane
nodes.name: transfer

nodes.documentation: approves the transfer of one plane to another person, to be called only by the origin owner
nodes.name: approve

nodes.documentation: takes ownership of a plane from another user, to be called by the intended recipient, requires prior approval by the original owner
nodes.name: takeOwnership
